{"tid":2183978,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"無力感？看鬼節的廣告吧 - 林夕","createTime":"2020-09-01T09:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T09:15:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c6cd5e9393b028118b4a898d20ded305055f083c","tid":2183978,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:10:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200901/4NHP452BD5EODASUXZVBVJJN4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200901%2F4NHP452BD5EODASUXZVBVJJN4M%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7vPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=e7d941f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200901%2F4NHP452BD5EODASUXZVBVJJN4M%2F&h=239e0329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200901/4NHP452BD5EODASUXZVBVJJN4M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n無力感？看鬼節的廣告吧 - 林夕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pt-iJvAOZuzkSSrot0uUg5iRM2I=/1262x850/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y6RZBYCV3ZH3REEF7Y5IV7W35M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fpt-iJvAOZuzkSSrot0uUg5iRM2I%3D%2F1262x850%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY6RZBYCV3ZH3REEF7Y5IV7W35M.png&h=028ac64b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬼節當前，如果說我建議大家上網把今年#全聯#中元節廣告三輯、每輯四篇共十二篇看完，只不過共六分鐘時間，會讓我們從「無力感」得到力量，一點都沒誇張。且看《明達與水鬼的世紀對談》吧。本人私人解讀如下：<br />\n<br />\n「抓交替」篇。。。。。。。。。。。。。。年輕人問鬼：「那你真的有在抓交替嗎」，鬼曰：「你有那麼好抓嗎」，然後提醒年輕人：「不管是颱風季節，或是水裏的暗流多，小心一點」，是的，浪高時只要不走到水位的紅線，如水靈動，別作無意識冒險，別做無意義犧牲，水鬼還能怎麼樣？<br />\n<br />\n「浪」篇。年輕人說「上次那道浪，超讚的，好不容易追到了，結果沒站好，超可惜的」。。。。。。。。。。。。鬼勸說：「你現在要做的，就是要做好準備，耐心等待下一個」，聽到了，無力感？先準備好，充實自己吧。<br />\n<br />\n「做人做事」篇。鬼問：「。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「勇敢」篇。鬼問：「你會怕鬼嗎」，。。。。。。。。。。。。只要面對面久了，就知道恐怖的本質，你不怕它，它就不可怕。對啦，那水鬼就寄語年輕人：「面對你還害怕的事情，才會變得勇敢」，香港年輕人足夠勇敢了，只是水鬼說，還有更大的浪在後面，勇氣也是一次再一次累積下來，沒人天生就是有智慧的勇者。<br />\n<br />\n全聯這系列廣告，我私心認為也有撐香港的意思，無力感者萬勿錯過。"},{"pid":"35fe688c74a2ff3d92eb94da4ed46ff759b4e9ad","tid":2183978,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:15:18.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}